Global Cannabis Lighting Market Insights
Cannabis Lighting Market size was valued at USD 4.85 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.50 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.10% from 2024 to 2030.

Cannabis Lighting Market Overview
The global Cannabis Lighting Market is expected to reach USD 6.21 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 17.3% from 2021 to 2028. The increasing legalization of cannabis in various regions and the growing demand for high-quality cannabis products have propelled the market. LED lighting is the dominant technology segment due to its energy efficiency and cost-effectiveness. The market growth is also influenced by innovations in lighting systems that improve plant growth and optimize energy consumption. Additionally, the rise of indoor cultivation is another factor contributing to the market's expansion.

